		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I can think of at least three other reasons to make a repro:
<br />
<br />1. Technical curiosity, i.e. can it be done?
<br />2. You want a cartridge version of the game in your collection but you don't want to pay a premium for the real deal.
<br />3. You want to play it on real hardware. Yes, even if it's bad.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


