		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Post subject:&nbsp;</td>
		<td><b></b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Cheethahmen 2, in true Active Enterprises style, is a multicart where each level is a separate 32k program and 8k graphics bank.  You can turn each level into a separate Mapper 0 ROM image, and they will play in almost any emulator (even Nesticle).
<br />
<br />Caveman Games also used the Multicart approach to game implementation.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


